/*!
    \title Line segment
    \ingroup quickgraphlibdemos
    \brief Finite line segments in data coordinates.
    \example linesegment

    \image examples/LineSegment.png

    This example demonstrates using LineSegment to draw finite segments between two points in data coordinates. The red segment is paired with a LineSegmentRoi so it can be selected, moved by dragging its body and resized by dragging its endpoint handles. The other segments demonstrate standard ShapePath styling properties such as stroke width, dashing and cap style.

    \quotefile examples/LineSegment.qml
*/
